# Unity generated
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/

# Asset meta data should only be ignored when the corresponding asset is also ignored
!/[Aa]ssets/**/*.meta

# The [Bb]uild/ rule above accidentally ignores a source folder inside the unity-mcp
# package (Editor/Tools/Build). Re-include it so its scripts are committed.
!/Packages/com.coplaydev.unity-mcp/Editor/Tools/Build/
!/Packages/com.coplaydev.unity-mcp/Editor/Tools/Build/**

# Uncomment this line if you wish to ignore the asset store tools plugin
# /[Aa]ssets/AssetStoreTools*

# Autogenerated VS/MD solution and project files
ExportedObj/
.consulo/
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# Unity3D generated meta files
*.pidb.meta
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb.meta

# Unity3D generated file on crash reports
sysinfo.txt

# Builds
*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa
*.unitypackage
*.app

# Crashlytics
crashlytics-build.properties

# Packed Addressables
/[Aa]ssets/[Aa]ddressable[Aa]ssets[Dd]ata/*/*.bin*

# Temporary auto-generated Android Assets
/[Aa]ssets/[Ss]treamingAssets/aa.meta
/[Aa]ssets/[Ss]treamingAssets/aa/*

# JetBrains Rider
.idea/

# Visual Studio Code
.vscode/

# AI-assisted iteration screenshots
/Assets/Screenshots/
# Accidental nested blank Unity project
/My project/

# macOS
.DS_Store
